# Testing

- Unit tests per service and repository.
- Mock Prisma in service tests — test business logic in isolation.
- API e2e tests for critical flows: auth, resume upload, job CRUD.
- Test file co-located: `users.service.spec.ts` next to `users.service.ts`.
- No snapshot tests for UI — prefer behavior assertions.
